# Performance mods for Forge 1.20.1

## Optimization

These mods directly improve modpack performance through code optimizations. 

| Name                                                                                                   | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                | Additional Notes                                                                                                                                                              | Alternatives                                                                                                                                 |
| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| [Alternate Current](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alternate-current)                    | Vanilla-compatible redstone optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                  | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Connectivity](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/connectivity)                              | Fix Login timeouts, Packet sizes errors, Payloads errors, ghostblocks and more                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                                                             | [Packet Fixer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/packet-fixer)                                                                    |
| [Dynamic FPS](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamic-fps)                                | Improve performance when Minecraft is in the background                                                                                                                                                                    | -                                                                                                                                                                             | [FPS Reducer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fps-reducer)                                                                      |
| [Bobby Reforged](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bobby-reforged)                          | Allows for render distances greater than the server's view-distance setting                                                                                                                                                | -                                                                                                                                                                             | [Farsight](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/farsight), though this mod lacks a chunk caching feature.                            |
| [Embeddium](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/embeddium)*                                   | Rendering optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                                    | -                                                                                                                                                                             | [Xenon](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/xenon)                                                                                  |
| [FastFurnace](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fastfurnace)                                | A performance upgrade for the furnace                                                                                                                                                                                      | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [FastSuite](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fastsuite)                                    | A performance upgrade for the JSON recipe system                                                                                                                                                                           | -                                                                                                                                                                             | [Recipe Essentials](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/recipe-essentials-forge-fabric)                                             |
| [FastWorkbench](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fastworkbench)                            | A performance upgrade for the crafting table                                                                                                                                                                               | Adds tooltips to Crafting Tables while the mod is installed. Can be disabled by going to `config/fastbench.cfg` and setting `"Disable tooltip on crafting table"` to `false`. | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [FerriteCore](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ferritecore)*                               | Memory usage optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                                 | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Flerovium](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/flerovium)                                    | Greatly improve your fps with virtually no side-effects on graphics quality                                                                                                                                                | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Gnetum](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/gnetum)                                          | Distribute HUD updates over multiple frames to improve performance                                                                                                                                                         | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [ImmediatelyFast](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immediatelyfast)                        | Speeds up immediate mode rendering in Minecraft                                                                                                                                                                            | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Ixeris](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ixeris)                                          | Buffered raw input and threaded event polling                                                                                                                                                                              | -                                                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                            |
| [Radium Reforged](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/radium-reforged)*                       | An optimization mod for Minecraft which improves server performance significantly.                                                                                                                                         | -                                                                                                                                                                             | [Canary](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/canary), though this mod is considered exceedingly worse for performance and stability |
| [Modernfix](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/modernfix)*                                   | All-in-one mod that improves performance, reduces memory usage, and fixes many bugs                                                                                                                                        | Enabling [Dynamic Resources](https://github.com/embeddedt/ModernFix/wiki/Dynamic-Resources-FAQ) can halve RAM usage                                                           | -                                                                                                                                            |
